reviewText: Not a bad DVD.  Other reviewers warned that it was a bit extreme, but that is largely a matter of opinion--I would not let that stop anyone from purchasing.  I like this DVD and found Mistress Tara quite good.  I wish the girl she was working with had been more vocal, but I would rather have silence than overacting.  Overall I would recommend if this DVD fits into your genre.
